nodes.text: The folded ear boosqueak was a rare, arboreal species that was native to the forested planet Fedje, located within the Atrivis sector of the Outer Rim Territories. Fedje was noted for its exotic lifeforms, as exemplified by the creature.

The folded ear boosqueak was created for the strategy game Star Wars: Rebellion, produced by LucasArts in 1998. It was mentioned in the in-game encyclopedia entry for the planet Fedje, as an example of one of the "many forms of exotic arboreal lifeforms" native to the planet.
